        <abstract> 
<p>Sends his MS of orchid paper ["A few notes on the fecundation of orchids and their morphology", <hi rend="italic">J. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Bot.)</hi> 8 (1865): 127–35] for CD to send to an editor.</p>  
<p>CD was right about <hi rend="italic">Catasetum</hi> sexes.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Ficus</hi> experiments fail.</p> 
        </abstract>
